    "Dates written in the form of multiple words are assigned separate NEs for each word, instead of treating it as a single NE.",
    "The system offers no support to handle the segmentation problem in the Urdu language which commonly occurs due to differences in writing styles.",
    "Riaz et al.",
    "[39] use the rules specified for six NE types including person name, organization, location, numbers, date, and designation.",
    "They evaluate their approach on 2,262 documents taken from the Becker-Riaz corpus [49] that contain news stories."
  ],
